## ğŸ”§ DEPENDENCIES TO INSTALL

Add to `functions/package.json`:

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@sendgrid/mail": "^7.7.0",
    "openai": "^4.20.0",
    "puppeteer": "^21.5.0"
  }
}
```

Then run:
```bash
cd functions
npm install
```

